('a0ed67fe-c6a5-59a7-aea9-a58a2085a29c', '56238401-177a-4cd9-9b27-e81206fe4ed7', 'The two research findings are remarkably ___, even though they were conducted by different teams.', '儘管是由不同的團隊進行的，但這兩項研究結果卻非常相似。', 'alike', 'acute', 'ample', 'aloof', 'a- (趨向/處於某種狀態) + like (相似的) → 處於相似的狀態 → 相似的。', 'a + like → 變得像一樣 → 相似的。', '2026-07-06 19:49:34', '2026-07-06 19:49:34'),
